represent a T √ó K matrix, where K is the number of
the latent topics and each row in Œ∏ describes the distribution of one tag belonging to the latent topics. Let œà
represent a K √ó V distribution matrix, where each row
is a distribution vector of one topic over words and V
is the number of words in the dictionary of D.
