Changing TraÔ¨Éc: We also tested the performance of AFD
under changing traÔ¨Éc conditions. In this scenario, three Ô¨Çow
groups (AIMD1, Binomial2, TCP) begin sending data at the
start of the simulation. After 100 seconds, three additional
