‚Ä¢ Quantizing. The continuous yÃÇ[n] is then mapped to the
discrete video bitrate r[n] ‚àà R, possibly with the help of
side information such as client buffer size, etc.
‚Ä¢ Scheduling. The algorithm selects the target interval until
the next download request, TÃÇ [n].
